    Scope and Contents
Experimental films made by students under David Viera's instruction.  Notable is Michael Evan's "Communication at SSU or Whipped Cream Pie."  The two audio tapes are soundtracks for the Super 8 films.  Included are 25 commercials for Kendall/Curity, Sears, Kraft, London Fog, and Kinney.  
  
